The source code in packages/envd/ and packages/shared/ is forked from
e2b-dev/infra (commit 7f3e661c8c1da50c3be5f34ca502c4f2fbe7d4c4, 2026-05-14)
and modified for MaxiCore by Helix12 Labs.

Modifications include:
- Module path renamed from github.com/e2b-dev/infra/packages/* to
  github.com/Helix12-Labs/helix12-maxicore-envd/packages/*
- Subset extraction (envd + 6 shared/pkg dependencies: filesystem, httpserver,
  id, keys, smap, utils — orchestrator + other packages excluded)
- MaxiCore-specific build pipeline (Docker + GitHub Actions)
- MaxiCore-specific systemd unit (envd.service)
- MaxiCore-specific MMDS integration via sandbox-manager

Files modified for MaxiCore have a "Modified by Helix12-Labs YYYY-MM-DD" comment
in their header. Unmodified files retain their original e2b copyright headers
unchanged.

